r<br></li><li>Character customization (+Steam Inventory)<br></li><li>Ingame mod editor with live scripting support<br></li><li>Steam Workshop for gamemodes and maps<br></li><li>Replay saving<br></li><li>High quality bass music as original soundtrack</li></ul>",
